Simulator Options
-----------------

--task [simulator operation]
   6 Edit Distance

-B [sub-task]
   0  Edit distance calculation (default)
   32 Algorithms comparison
   64 g(n) Estimation with bounded error on difference

-f [flags]
   Edit distance calculation
   0  Sample, Linear (default)
   1  Exhaustive
   5  Exhaustive with min and max centers 
   4  Sample, Linear and info (prototype)
   14 Sample, Quadratic and Info  
   32 Bounded error on e(n)
   64 Bounded error on difference 2e(n/2) - e(n) 